                    <span>Not only does this book cover network essentials, it is presented in a way that actually promotes learning (!)  While this may seem an obvious goal, the author of this book clearly puts great effort into presenting the information in a meaningful way (most books on this subject lack this care). I'd highly recommend this to students, or even to practicioners who would like a refresher or general reference on data communications.</span>
                  
              
